text: I love Ten, and I was so excited that he would do a solo release, but so far I'm deeply disappointed, even though his performance is great. The style of this looks too much like Jungkook's "Standing Next To You", and the Matrix is overused, eg also in Minho's "Heartbreak". He deserves much better! I'm also disappointed that he sings in English, although I admit since he is Thai and speaks English well it at least makes more sense to choose English rather than Korean or Thai, because the audience wouldn't be used to that.
